headline: Paycom Announces Quarterly Cash Dividend
summary: OKLAHOMA CITY, February 10, 2025--Paycom Software, Inc. ("Paycom") (NYSE: PAYC), a leading provider of comprehensive, cloud-based human capital management software, announced today that its Board of Directors declared a cash dividend in the amount of $0.375 per share of common stock, to be paid on March 24, 2025, to all stockholders of record as of the close of business on March 10, 2025.
